Part 7: Validation

Run:

make scripts-chmod
make help
make scripts-list
make server-status || true
make git-safe-status
make validate-fast

Acceptance criteria:
- make validate-fast passes.
- make help shows new server and git-safe targets.
- no duplicate target warnings.
- no Makefile.bak.* tracked.
- no old backend port 8000 runtime source references.
- no secret-looking values in tracked runtime/source files.
- server-start and server-stop are idempotent.
- stop-local.sh only kills PIDs it created.
- production wrapper scripts fail safely if /opt/zdash/runtime is absent.